An opensource minimalistic multi account twitter client for Chrome.

Just an alpha version, please don't expect too much.

With Twic now you can:
* Add as much accounts as you want
* Read the home timeline
* Write your tweets
* Reply (+ to all), retweet (+ oldschool), undo retweet
* Delete your own tweets
* Get some info about user profiles
* Follow/unfollow users

Changelog:
https://github.com/silentroach/twic/blob/master/Changelog

---

Feel free to help develop or translate/correct Twic. Just mail me
